2017;;Youth in Oregon;;American;;Joel David Moore;;Joel David Moore (director); Andrew Eisen (screenplay); Frank Langella, Billy Crudup, Christina Applegate, Nicola Peltz, Josh Lucas, Mary Kay Place, Alex Shaffer;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Youth_in_Oregon;;A man is tasked with driving his embittered 80-year-old father-in-law cross country to be legally euthanized in Oregon, while along the way helping him rediscover a reason for living.